                           </VBox.margin>
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="45.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Define the scope of the project: This includes identifying the business processes that will be reengineered and the goals of the project." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="46.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Assess the current state of the business process: This involves analyzing the current process to understand how it works and identify opportunities for improvement." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="32.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Identify key stakeholders: These are the people who will be affected by the changes and will need to be involved in the process." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="46.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Design the new business process: This involves creating a detailed plan for the redesigned process, including the steps involved, the resources required, and the value added by each step." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="46.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Implement the new process: This involves implementing the new process and making any necessary changes to systems, structures, and culture." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label prefHeight="46.0" prefWidth="843.0" text="Monitor and review the process: This involves tracking the performance of the new process to ensure it is meeting the goals of the project and making any necessary adjustments." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrapText="true">
